TITLE: Object Transformation with Object.fromEntries in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to transform objects by combining Object.entries with array methods like filter and map.
SOURCE: https://github.com/v8/v8.dev/blob/main/src/features/object-fromentries.md#2025-04-10_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const object = { x: 42, y: 50, abc: 9001 };
const result = Object.fromEntries(
  Object.entries(object)
    .filter(([ key, value ]) => key.length === 1)
    .map(([ key, value ]) => [ key, value * 2 ])
);
// â†’ { x: 84, y: 100 }
