TITLE: Comparing Function Parameter Handling with and without Rest Operator in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the difference between handling variable arguments using the traditional arguments object versus the ES2015 rest operator. The rest operator provides a cleaner syntax for working with an indefinite number of function arguments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/v8/v8.dev/blob/main/src/blog/v8-release-47.md#2025-04-10_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
