TITLE: Implementing Promise Chain with Duplicate Cleanup
DESCRIPTION: Traditional promise implementation showing duplicate cleanup code in both then() and catch() blocks for handling loading spinner state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/v8/v8.dev/blob/main/src/features/promise-finally.md#2025-04-10_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
