TITLE: Async Generator Function for Reading Lines (ES2015+)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates an async generator function using proposed async iterator syntax. It shows how concise and readable advanced ES2015+ features can be.
SOURCE: https://github.com/v8/v8.dev/blob/main/src/blog/high-performance-es2015.md#2025-04-10_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
async function* readLines(path) {
  let file = await fileOpen(path);
  try {
    while (!file.EOF) {
      yield await file.readLine();
    }
  } finally {
    await file.close();
  }
}
```

