TITLE: Demonstrating Scope in Static Initialization Blocks in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how static initialization blocks have their own variable scope. It demonstrates the use of 'this' referring to the class constructor and 'super' for accessing the parent class's static properties.
