SOURCE: https://github.com/v8/v8.dev/blob/main/src/blog/spread-elements.md#2025-04-10_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function clone(arr) {
  // Pre-allocate the correct number of elements, to avoid
  // having to grow the array.
  const result = new Array(arr.length);
  for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
    result[i] = arr[i];
  }
  return result;
}
```

