TITLE: Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty Algorithm Without Shorthand Notation
DESCRIPTION: The expanded algorithm for Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty without using '?' and '!' shorthands. This shows explicit Completion Record handling at each step.
